Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:44.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100413,104500}Then you also went\Nto the fortune teller Pandora…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105001,106002}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106419,107962}And when I came to…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108129,109964}…the ring, which was\Na family heirloom, was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111007,112592}It's the same trick as the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:56.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113384,116054}But, Sister! I'm sure of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:59.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116304,119098}The one who stole\Nthe ring is St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:01.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120224,121517}There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:08.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123561,128066}MOM'S ENEMY!\NROSEMARY'S CONSPIRACY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133571,135573}SERIAL ROBBERY\NBY SAINT TAIL CONTINUES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136324,139285}This is the longest\Nit's gone in Seika City's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:25.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140703,145333}I've heard that all of the victims\Nare saying St. Tail did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145875,147210}I don't know anything about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148503,150171}What a terrible thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150296,153383}My dad says\Nhe can't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154133,155760}I don't know…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158346,160890}There's no way that\Nshe would do these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175279,176364}Asuka Jr. …
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177281,178282}A warning note…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179450,181994}St. Tail's warning note\Nhasn't been delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184664,185623}We had an agreement…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186290,188042}…that she would give me\Na warning note every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189043,191337}She's never broken the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193005,194006}Promise…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194924,196676}Those newspaper articles…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197635,198594}I don't believe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203349,205643}Thank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210898,213192}It has to be hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214902,216237}All of the victims are…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216529,219741}…made to believe\Nthat St. Tail stole their things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221743,224287}That's the revenge\Non the Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224537,226080}In order to get\Nrevenge on my mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226205,227623}…she's giving me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228040,229000}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229083,230042}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231002,234297}Even though I thought it was\Ndisrespectful to your mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234964,238634}…I researched the old articles\Nabout Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242847,243806}This is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243931,245391}THIEF LUCIFER PUBLICLY\NCHALLENGES ROSEMARY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246225,248978}It looks like\NMysterious Thief Lucifer's warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250104,252106}Oh, Mom. What a showoff…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253149,254692}In this article, Rosemary…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:18.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254859,258237}…seemed to be Lucifer's\Nopponent, I mean, rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259489,261240}Yeah. I heard\Nabout her from Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261449,263075}She was like a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263951,265953}The person who resents\NLucifer can only be…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266287,267622}…this same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:31.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267872,271125}You're right. Mom returned\Nall of the items she had stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272585,274921}But this Rosemary…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275379,277548}…has some connection\Nwith that girl…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278633,281427}I'm going to Pandora again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282220,284722}I may find the location\Nof the victim's ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287308,290269}By the way, Seira,\Nhow do you pronounce this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305993,307411}FORTUNE TELLING
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307954,309664}I'm really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310331,311874}If the same thing\Nhappens to me again…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314335,315378}But I have to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316212,318047}For the sake\Nof St. Tail's reputation…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320591,322009}Excuse me…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328599,331018}Welcome!\NI've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331185,332436}PANDORA'S ORIGINAL GOODS\NMEDUSA CHAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:37.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333604,337275}You don't need to be\Nthat surprised! Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337400,338359}…Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346951,348119}Mom…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351372,352415}What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354834,356127}How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357003,358838}Mom! You've got\Nto get rid of that habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360339,361549}You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361716,364343}You look exactly like\NLucifer did at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366387,368681}But cuteness is only skin deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376522,379901}Lucifer… She loved doing\Nthings that people hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380318,382987}She always targeted\Nthe item I was planning to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383112,384780}She was like a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385865,387199}That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388367,390161}I've heard that\Nsomewhere before…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392705,395082}AIthough I don't have\Nany grudge against you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395207,397585}…you have to come along with me\Nso that I can get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398002,401047}Just curse the fates you were\Nborn as Lucifer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401839,402840}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403007,404216}Kabako…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404675,407094}KABA (HIPPOPOTAMUS) KO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409305,410473}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410848,412391}Oh, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412642,415102}You're Ms. Kabako Sendo,\Nalso known as Rosemary, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415770,417396}I learned how to read\Nyour name from Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417521,419523}Please don't address me\Nwith my ridiculous real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419649,420608}Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422985,425488}That horrible\Nwarning note from Lucifer…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:08.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425780,428908}Because of that,\Nthe public knew my real name…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428991,430159}…and people made fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430368,431327}That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431786,433162}The humiliation…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433454,435831}I've never, even for a second,\Nforgotten that feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437124,440670}Like mother, like daughter!\NHow hateful! I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441462,442880}I didn't mean anything by it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443297,445299}I just wanted to know\Nabout the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446258,448177}The stolen items are not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448970,452515}We don't know anything\Nabout the items St. Tail stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452640,453933}Right, Maju?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454058,455226}Right, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455351,456310}This mother and daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456852,458479}All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458938,460272}Sorry to have disturbed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462024,463442}Come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464527,466737}How infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467154,469156}I'm not afraid of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469699,471409}Who do they think they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471492,473077}Meimi, sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476706,479834}I checked for places\Nwhere a pair posing…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480126,482586}…as mother and daughter\Nhave moved in recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483087,484422}This is the only place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485381,487216}This is a monastery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487800,490594}Yes. It's the old building\Nalong the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491053,493806}It's not used now,\Nand it's supposed to be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494724,496350}It's been for sale\Nfor quite a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496684,499603}But people thought it was creepy\Nand didn't want to get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500104,501772}If those two are there…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501981,503315}…the stolen items\Nmust be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504316,505818}I'm going to get them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506402,508863}And I'll clear St. Tail's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510239,513951}For the sake of Asuka Jr., too,\Nwho believes in me…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522668,526338}Darn it! Someone else\Nmust be using St. Tail's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527339,529842}She must have been forced to be\Ninvolved in such a strange case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:55.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531719,535514}– That blimp!\N– Something is written on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537516,539101}"Tonight I'm going to the monastery…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539185,541479}…to take the rings and other things\Nwhich are in the possession…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541562,543314}…of Kabako Sendo,\Nalso known as Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543397,544398}– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545399,546859}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547193,548360}It's St. Tail's warning note!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549653,550738}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553908,557161}I used the same\Nwarning note as my mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557328,558287}Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558621,559622}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559914,562291}Oh, you're worrying\Nabout the location, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562458,564835}Asuka Jr. can figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564960,565961}It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567880,570382}Is it wise to show her real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574261,576305}Oh, no…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576639,578974}I was only thinking about doing\Nthe same thing as my mom did…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590444,592196}She is indeed\NLucifer's daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592279,594824}She has a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595449,597868}It doesn't matter whether\Nit's the mother or daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597993,599203}I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602206,603624}Your money's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604416,606293}Thank… Thank you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611215,613843}But who is Rosemary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614802,617930}Her last few messages\Nhave been difficult to understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620933,622643}What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623769,626355}I am Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626689,628691}How do you do, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630025,631610}You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635364,636657}Rosemary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643789,646959}This is jade dust…\NIt's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647751,649253}Don't take your eyes off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651005,653507}What's happening?\NI can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674111,677031}You don't need to worry about\Nnot understanding what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677156,678574}Cute little detective…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678991,682244}I'm inviting you to my house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682828,685623}So what are you\Ngoing to do, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686123,688584}Your weak point\Nis now in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689293,691587}You angered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692296,694882}You'll regret it,\Nand you'll wish you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:53.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710105,713275}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718447,719406}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:02.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721867,722868}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725329,727957}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745599,747184}Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747685,749687}Don't worry. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752231,755359}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755901,756860}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760948,761991}I wonder why…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762533,763784}I have a bad feeling about this…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:45.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764743,765703}Meimi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857169,858670}Asuka Jr. isn't here…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860422,861924}Nor is his security staff…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862257,864051}They couldn't fiind this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868889,871392}You… didn't come…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880818,881777}The item you're looking for…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881860,883278}…is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884655,887074}But no matter\Nhow much you search here…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887699,889201}…the detective won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891453,892704}Maju…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894164,895207}What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896667,897751}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898669,899670}You'll see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931410,933078}Don't be misled, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933287,934872}This is hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934955,936039}It's an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940335,941295}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942671,943672}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944756,946508}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949970,951096}lllusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966945,968655}She created\Na wind with her magic…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968947,970824}…and pushed away\Nmy hypnosis…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980417,981835}Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983128,985005}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987007,989092}Oh, weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989259,990385}You're in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990761,992638}Never mind that. Look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993430,996183}Can you tell who is next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997476,998852}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001021,1004066}This is a one-way mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004191,1006443}They can't see us\Nfrom the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006902,1008820}You'd better watch\Nclosely from here…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009780,1011907}…and see what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029299,1030300}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031510,1034346}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036014,1037266}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042896,1044064}It's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044982,1046316}Curtain ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055033,1056451}Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066503,1068589}What are you going to do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072134,1073135}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083604,1086607}I've gotten back\Neverything you stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088483,1089568}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090444,1091820}Please run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092863,1093822}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102748,1104458}Everyone has something…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104541,1107002}…that they don't want\Nother people to know…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107461,1110797}You do, too, daughter of Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119348,1122059}That was loud.\NIt sounds like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122517,1124394}Don't worry, Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124811,1127439}There is always an end\Nto everything and every storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127814,1129024}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130317,1132027}There is an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153048,1155384}She's very near. Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:20.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156385,1160055}I'll do the same to you, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180158,1182536}Until I catch you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187666,1189167}…don't get caught…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194047,1195006}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205142,1208687}You wanted to know\Nher identity, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214025,1215610}You're pleased, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239509,1241803}Why… Why…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246975,1251480}Meimi!
